        p.text-right.hidden
          a.btn.btn-inverse.btn-large(href='/code/') Start Coding »

      .row
        .span6
          h2 About the guide
          p
            | The course material is under development. <br/> Read about the guiding principles below.
          p
            a.btn.btn-inverse(href='how.html') Learn More »
