          h2 In Real Life
          p
            | The guide is augmented by weekly workshops at <a href="http://avopenstudios.com/">AV Open Studios</a> in Budapest, Hungary. Here we help students realize their artistic vision by providing technological guidance and assisting in the design and development of their projects.
          p
            a.btn.btn-primary(href='join.html') Join the Class »

